# 🚀 GitHub Actions CI/CD Pipeline for AethelFrame

This automation template handles **schema validation**, **async job dispatch**, **resilient polling**, **C2PA verification**, and **artifact publishing**. It's designed for both PR dry-runs and production rendering workflows.

---

## 📁 Repository Structure
```
.github/
  workflows/
    aethel-pipeline.yml      # Main CI/CD workflow
config/
  aethel_subject.json        # Pipeline configuration payload
scripts/
  aethel_runner.py           # CI orchestration script
```

---

## ⚙️ `aethel-pipeline.yml`

```yaml
name: 🎬 AethelFrame Pipeline Automation
on:
  workflow_dispatch:
    inputs:
      subject_name:
        description: Biographical Subject
        required: true
        default: 'Odin_Raven'
      quality:
        description: Render Quality
        type: choice
        options: [fast_preview, balanced, cinematic_high]
        default: balanced
      dry_run:
        description: Validate Only (No GPU Render)
        type: boolean
        default: false
  push:
    branches: [main, release/*]
    paths: ['config/aethel_*.json']

env:
  AETHEL_API_KEY: ${{ secrets.AETHEL_API_KEY }}
  AETHEL_BASE_URL: ${{ vars.AETHEL_BASE_URL || 'https://api.aethelframe.ai' }}
  PYTHON_VERSION: '3.11'
  AETHEL_MAX_WAIT_MIN: 180

jobs:
  pipeline:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    timeout-minutes: ${{ fromJson(vars.AETHEL_TIMEOUT || '360') }}
    outputs:
      job_id: ${{ steps.dispatch.outputs.job_id }}
      video_url: ${{ steps.download.outputs.video_url }}

    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4
      - uses: actions/setup-python@v5
        with: { python-version: ${{ env.PYTHON_VERSION }} }
      
      - name: Install Dependencies
        run: pip install httpx pydantic c2pa-tool-cli

      - name: 🔍 Validate & Dispatch
        id: dispatch
        env:
          DRY_RUN: ${{ github.event.inputs.dry_run || false }}
          QUALITY: ${{ github.event.inputs.quality || 'balanced' }}
          SUBJECT: ${{ github.event.inputs.subject_name || 'CI_Test_Subject' }}
        run: python scripts/aethel_runner.py dispatch

      - name: ⏳ Monitor Async Job
        if: ${{ !fromJson(env.DRY_RUN) && steps.dispatch.outputs.job_id }}
        run: python scripts/aethel_runner.py poll
        env:
          JOB_ID: ${{ steps.dispatch.outputs.job_id }}

      - name: 📦 Download & Verify Artifacts
        if: ${{ !fromJson(env.DRY_RUN) }}
        id: download
        run: python scripts/aethel_runner.py verify
        env:
          JOB_ID: ${{ steps.dispatch.outputs.job_id }}

      - name: 📤 Upload to GitHub Artifacts
        if: ${{ success() }}
        uses: actions/upload-artifact@v4
        with:
          name: aethel-render-${{ github.run_id }}
          path: ./aethel_output/
          retention-days: 30
```

