## 🔐 Repository Secrets & Variables Required

| Scope | Key | Value/Description |
|-------|-----|-------------------|
| **Secrets** | `AETHEL_API_KEY` | Production API key with `async` & `render` permissions |
| **Secrets** | `GITHUB_TOKEN` | Auto-injected; used for artifact uploads & releases |
| **Variables** | `AETHEL_BASE_URL` | API endpoint (default: `https://api.aethelframe.ai`) |
| **Variables** | `AETHEL_TIMEOUT` | GitHub Actions timeout in minutes (default: `360`) |

