## 🔄 Workflow Execution Flow

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Workflow Trigger] --> B{DRY_RUN?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Validate Schema]
    C --> D[Exit Success]
    B -->|No| E[Dispatch Async Job]
    E --> F[Save job_id to GITHUB_STATE]
    F --> G[Poll /v1/jobs/:id]
    G --> H{Status?}
    H -->|completed| I[Download MP4 + C2PA Manifest]
    H -->|failed| J[Exit with Error Code]
    I --> K[Verify C2PA Hash/Signature]
    K --> L[Upload to GitHub Artifacts]
```

